*''Sagan om Ringen: Rollspelet'', the Swedish edition of ''[[Middle-earth Role Playing]]'' .
*''[[Sagan om Ringen (1971 film)]]'', the 1971 Swedish television film adaption of ''[[The Fellowship of the Ring]]''
